</ul>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Firestorm&action=edit&section=6.php.html" title="Edit section: Notes">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Notes">Notes</span></h2>
<div class="reflist references-column-count references-column-count-2" style="-moz-column-count: 2; -webkit-column-count: 2; column-count: 2; list-style-type: decimal;">
<ol class="references">
<li id="cite_note-AD673703_1961.2C_pg_8_.26_9-1"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-AD673703_1961.2C_pg_8_.26_9_1-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-AD673703_1961.2C_pg_8_.26_9_1-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.dtic.mil/cgi-bin/GetTRDoc?AD=AD673703&Location=U2&doc=GetTRDoc.pdf">http://www.dtic.mil/cgi-bin/GetTRDoc?AD=AD673703&amp;Location=U2&amp;doc=GetTRDoc.pdf</a> Problems of fire in Nuclear Warfare 1961, pg 8 &amp; 9.</span></li>
